    "fa": "As for the right of the wife, know that Allah made her your tranquility and comfort. Know this is Allah's blessing, so honour her and be gentle. Though your right over her is greater, she has the right to compassion, for she is your captive whom you feed and clothe, and when she errs in ignorance, you pardon her.",
